        <briefdescription>
<para>Apply the control value with min-max filtering. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Passes values through unchanged until the ring buffer is full. Once full, each new value triggers:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Buffer update (overwrites oldest value)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Recalculation of chunk maximums and minimums</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Output = (minimax + maximin) / 2</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>value</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Input control value, range -1000..1000 </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
